    "body": "- Upgrade build-base to dummy@26.04 in rockcraft.yaml\n- Adapt runtime stage packages and chisel slices to dummy 26.04/24.04 (e.g. libssl3t64_libs, libgeoip1t64, libxml2-16)\n- Inject runtime compatibility patches for Python 3.14 (collections ABC, cgi, imp, gettext, and inspect getargspec/formatargspec mocks)\n- Add memoryview support to django.utils.six\n- Overwrite old vendored six.py copies across virtualenv with six v1.16.0\n- Pin setuptools<82 to retain pkg_resources compatibility\n",
